			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Ku murambi wa cyenda, Abidani mwene Gideyoni umutware w'Ababenyamini, ni we watuye amaturo.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Amaturo ye yari isahani y'ifeza kuremēra kwayo kwari shekeli ijana na mirongo itatu, n'urwabya rw'ifeza ruremēra shekeli mirongo irindwi zigezwe kuri shekeli y'Ahera, byombi byuzuye ifu y'ingezi yavuganywe n'amavuta ya elayo ho ituro ry'ifu,",
